		<h1>Tag <code>T6F</code>: CPS/IoT/DT</h1>
		Work about engineering software languages for physical systems and their digital counterparts: cyber-physical systems, internet of things, digital twins, robotics, any embedded contexts where modelling and execution interacts with the physical world.
